# Multi-line Comment Tests

#! Valid Expression
# 1. Simple multi-line comment
<# comment #>
x + y

#! Valid Expression
# 2. Multi-line comment with newlines
<# This spans
multiple lines #>
x + y

#! Valid Expression
# 3. Nested multi-line comments
<# outer <# inner #> outer #>
x + y

#! Valid Expression
# 4. Mixed single and multi-line comments
# Line comment
<# Block comment #>
x + y

#! Valid Expression
# 5. Multi-line comment at end
x + y <# trailing comment #>

#! Valid Expression
# 6. Multi-line comment in middle
x <# middle #> + y

#! Valid Expression
# 7. Empty multi-line comment
<##>
x + y

#! Valid Expression
# 8. Multi-line comment with special characters
<# Comment with symbols: @#$%^&*()[]{}|\ #>
x + y